and we have spent hours and hours—hundreds&nbsp;
of hours—practicing, learning, and seeing&nbsp;&nbsp;

00:04:31.680 --> 00:04:38.120
applications of this Hindu-Arabic system.&nbsp;
So it's really almost hardwired into our&nbsp;&nbsp;

00:04:38.120 --> 00:04:47.880
mental frameworks, and we shouldn't take that for&nbsp;
granted. Okay, it's actually not a replacement for&nbsp;&nbsp;

00:04:47.880 --> 00:04:54.440
a solid logical foundation for what actually these&nbsp;
