00:04:54.440 --> 00:05:01.520
We all know that we can, you know, do Hindu-Arabic&nbsp;
arithmetic, at least for relatively small numbers&nbsp;&nbsp;

00:05:01.520 --> 00:05:07.120
where the calculator is not needed. But what&nbsp;
